<font color="#00ff00">you're on speakerphone. </font><font color="#ffff00">All right.</font>

30:29.440 --> 30:33.318
<font color="#00ff00">I isolated the tyre marks</font>
<font color="#00ff00">from Mayhew Farm.</font>

30:33.320 --> 30:36.838
<font color="#00ff00">Most prominent</font>
<font color="#00ff00">tread is a Realto Performo,</font>

30:36.840 --> 30:39.318
<font color="#00ff00">not many circulating in the UK</font>

30:39.320 --> 30:42.158
<font color="#00ff00">since they were bought out</font>
<font color="#00ff00">by Goodyear in 2015.</font>

30:42.160 --> 30:43.518
<font color="#ffff00">All right, great stuff.</font>

30:43.520 --> 30:45.838
<font color="#ffff00">Any chance you can fire me</font>
<font color="#ffff00">over the isolated tread?</font>

30:45.840 --> 30:49.958
<font color="#00ff00">I already have. And the green</font>
<font color="#00ff00">fabric from the fence -</font>

30:49.960 --> 30:53.278
<font color="#00ff00">65% poly, 35% cotton mix</font>

30:53.280 --> 30:56.238
<font color="#00ff00">with a distinctive</font>
<font color="#00ff00">anti-static grid weave.</font>

30:56.240 --> 30:58.358
<font color="#00ffff">Distinctive enough to source?</font>

30:58.360 --> 31:02.278
<font color="#00ff00">My money's on heavy-duty overalls,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">but no joy on a make,</font>

31:02.280 --> 31:03.518
<font color="#00ff00">not so the stain.</font>

31:03.520 --> 31:08.358
<font color="#00ff00">It's a graphite lubricant,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">specifically designed for locks.</font>

31:08.360 --> 31:12.438
<font color="#00ff00">Apparently superior</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to wet oils and WD40,</font>

31:12.440 --> 31:15.558
<font color="#00ff00">the brand name is Bixley. </font><font color="#ffff00">Bixley.</font>

31:15.560 --> 31:16.840
<font color="#ffff00">Got it.</font>

31:31.680 --> 31:34.478
<font color="#ffff00">Realto Performo - all of them.</font>

31:34.480 --> 31:35.878
<font color="#00ff00">Yeah.</font>

31:35.880 --> 31:38.800
<font color="#00ff00">Too narrow for our tyre mark. </font><font color="#ffff00">Yeah.</font>

31:40.920 --> 31:42.440
<font color="#ffff00">Ours was more like that.</font>

31:53.600 --> 31:57.000
<font color="#00ff00">Nice rig. Did Malcolm ever take it</font>
<font color="#00ff00">out?</font>

31:58.240 --> 32:01.598
<font color="#ffffff">No. </font><font color="#00ff00">Yeah, didn't think so.</font>

32:01.600 --> 32:03.000
<font color="#ffff00">That's a lot of tyres.</font>

32:04.720 --> 32:05.960
<font color="#ffffff">Realto went under.</font>

32:07.120 --> 32:10.600
<font color="#ffffff">The distributor's down the road</font>
<font color="#ffffff">there. </font><font color="#ffff00">Going cheap? </font><font color="#ffffff">Yeah.</font>

32:11.880 --> 32:15.240
<font color="#ffff00">Where does Malcolm do his off-site</font>
<font color="#ffff00">locksmithing since he moved in?</font>

32:45.800 --> 32:49.160
<font color="#ffffff">Do you want to see down here</font>
<font color="#ffffff">or what? </font><font color="#ffff00">Yeah.</font>

33:10.840 --> 33:15.198
<font color="#ffff00">The green fabric you found is likely</font>
<font color="#ffff00">from a boiler suit -</font>

33:15.200 --> 33:18.720
<font color="#ffff00">the oil staining it</font>
<font color="#ffff00">is Bixley's lubricant.</font>

33:32.360 --> 33:34.198
<font color="#ffff00">Can't see any tear.</font>

33:34.200 --> 33:36.720
<font color="#00ff00">Could have a couple spare. </font><font color="#ffff00">Maybe.</font>

33:38.160 --> 33:40.880
<font color="#00ff00">And... </font><font color="#ffff00">Why not new phone?</font>

33:41.920 --> 33:43.560
<font color="#ffff00">Hard to do his job without one.</font>

33:48.200 --> 33:50.358
<font color="#ffffff">Was Wilde placed under surveillance?</font>

33:50.360 --> 33:51.678
<font color="#00ffff">Yeah.</font>

33:51.680 --> 33:54.718
<font color="#ffffff">When? </font><font color="#00ffff">Two weeks, mid-October.</font>

33:54.720 --> 33:57.638
<font color="#00ffff">Why? </font><font color="#ffffff">Just wondering how he kept</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Jason hidden away</font>

33:57.640 --> 33:59.718
<font color="#ffffff">when he was the subject of</font>
<font color="#ffffff">so much attention.</font>

33:59.720 --> 34:01.320
<font color="#ffffff">PHONE RINGS</font>

34:02.680 --> 34:04.998
<font color="#00ffff">Hi. I can't talk at the moment.</font>

34:05.000 --> 34:06.640
<font color="#00ffff">Can it wait until tonight?</font>

34:08.080 --> 34:09.440
<font color="#00ffff">Martin.</font>

34:11.440 --> 34:13.080
<font color="#00ffff">OK. Come on up.</font>

34:15.320 --> 34:16.878
<font color="#00ffff">Sorry, Nikki.</font>

34:16.880 --> 34:19.078
<font color="#00ffff">Is there an office</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that I can borrow?</font>

34:19.080 --> 34:20.120
<font color="#00ffff">My husband...</font>

34:21.520 --> 34:22.760
<font color="#00ffff">..is here.</font>

34:24.719 --> 34:25.960
<font color="#ffffff">Sure.</font>

34:31.280 --> 34:33.159
<font color="#ffff00">Hi, darling. </font><font color="#00ffff">Hi.</font>

34:34.800 --> 34:36.638
<font color="#00ffff">This is Dr Alexander.</font>

34:36.639 --> 34:38.239
<font color="#ffff00">Oh. </font><font color="#ffffff">Hi.</font>

34:42.960 --> 34:46.438
<font color="#ffffff">Look, I told you,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that's his old charger.</font>

34:46.440 --> 34:48.118
<font color="#ffffff">He doesn't have a phone.</font>

34:48.120 --> 34:50.800
<font color="#00ff00">Yeah, I thought you'd say that.</font>

35:05.880 --> 35:08.438
<font color="#00ff00">I get it, Robert.</font>

35:08.440 --> 35:10.838
<font color="#00ff00">You're trying to protect your son.</font>

35:10.840 --> 35:13.198
<font color="#00ff00">I'd do the same if I was in your</font>
<font color="#00ff00">shoes.</font>

35:13.200 --> 35:17.398
<font color="#00ff00">But, by him running away,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">he's just digging his hole deeper.</font>

35:17.400 --> 35:20.040
<font color="#ffff00">How did you come by those scratches</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on your neck?</font>

35:23.280 --> 35:26.318
<font color="#ffffff">Some moron kicked</font>
<font color="#ffffff">off about his MOT bill.</font>

35:26.320 --> 35:27.478
<font color="#ffff00">Right.</font>

35:27.480 --> 35:31.078
<font color="#ffff00">It's just...scratches like those</font>
<font color="#ffff00">suggest you were the aggressor.</font>

35:31.080 --> 35:33.958
<font color="#ffffff">Called me a prick. I lamped him.</font>

35:33.960 --> 35:37.840
<font color="#00ff00">So it wasn't any adjustment issues</font>
<font color="#00ff00">with Malcolm moving back home?</font>

35:40.280 --> 35:42.358
<font color="#00ff00">We just want to talk to him, Robert.</font>

35:42.360 --> 35:46.600
<font color="#00ff00">The sooner that happens,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the better, especially for him.</font>

35:53.040 --> 35:54.160
<font color="#ffffff">This village...</font>

35:55.520 --> 35:57.160
<font color="#ffffff">..it's his whole world.</font>

35:58.160 --> 35:59.640
<font color="#ffffff">Mine, too.</font>

36:01.320 --> 36:02.720
<font color="#ffffff">And we're finished here.</font>

36:05.760 --> 36:07.440
<font color="#ffffff">Finished.</font>

36:10.560 --> 36:12.040
<font color="#ffffff">Last number dialled.</font>

36:28.240 --> 36:29.558
<font color="#ffffff">Are you OK?</font>

36:29.560 --> 36:30.920
<font color="#00ffff">I just need to get some air.</font>

36:32.000 --> 36:34.120
<font color="#00ffff">He was asking me to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">step down as SIO.</font>

36:36.320 --> 36:39.118
<font color="#ffffff">Wow. </font><font color="#00ffff">Maybe this is selfish,</font>

36:39.120 --> 36:41.558
<font color="#00ffff">but I have given everything</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to this case.</font>

36:41.560 --> 36:43.680
<font color="#00ffff">I've lived and breathed</font>
<font color="#00ffff">it since September.</font>

36:44.800 --> 36:48.758
<font color="#00ffff">And I promised Tina and Pete</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that I would get them justice.</font>

36:48.760 --> 36:51.040
<font color="#00ffff">We can't give up, not now.</font>

36:53.000 --> 36:54.720
<font color="#ffffff">Congratulations, by the way.</font>

36:55.920 --> 36:57.120
<font color="#00ffff">Thanks.</font>

36:58.280 --> 37:01.918
<font color="#00ffff">We're very fortunate.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">We don't exactly rely on my salary</font>

37:01.920 --> 37:04.000
<font color="#00ffff">for our next meal, so...</font>

37:05.000 --> 37:08.240
<font color="#00ffff">..the way my husband sees it...</font>
<font color="#ffffff">There's no need for you to work.</font>

37:09.800 --> 37:11.200
<font color="#00ffff">Not now.</font>

37:16.080 --> 37:17.760
<font color="#00ffff">Do you have children?</font>

37:18.840 --> 37:20.958
<font color="#ffffff">No. No, I don't.</font>

37:20.960 --> 37:22.520
<font color="#00ffff">Is there a Mr Nikki?</font>

37:24.640 --> 37:25.800
<font color="#ffffff">Er...</font>

37:26.960 --> 37:28.878
<font color="#ffffff">..yeah.</font>

37:28.880 --> 37:30.920
<font color="#00ffff">Took way too long to answer that.</font>

37:35.080 --> 37:37.318
<font color="#ffffff">Are you ready to tell me</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the real reason</font>

37:37.320 --> 37:38.718
<font color="#ffffff">why you ditched the local lab?</font>

37:38.720 --> 37:41.480
<font color="#00ffff">The decision was taken</font>
<font color="#00ffff">over my head, Nikki.</font>

37:42.720 --> 37:44.000
<font color="#ffffff">MESSAGE ALERT</font>

37:47.520 --> 37:49.840
<font color="#00ffff">Got a current mobile for Malcolm.</font>

37:53.120 --> 37:55.798
<font color="#00ff00">It's just pinging off one mast.</font>

37:55.800 --> 37:57.558
<font color="#00ff00">The M4.</font>

37:57.560 --> 37:59.438
<font color="#00ff00">It's a rural area.</font>

37:59.440 --> 38:01.038
<font color="#ffffff">He's static.</font>

38:01.040 --> 38:05.080
<font color="#ffffff">He's not on the motorway.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Which basically leaves one location.</font>

38:11.400 --> 38:12.438
<font color="#ffffff">RINGING TONE</font>

38:12.440 --> 38:16.198
<font color="#00ff00">Boss? </font><font color="#00ffff">Where are you?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">En route to Lyell.</font>

38:16.200 --> 38:19.238
<font color="#00ffff">We think he's at Dinton Services.</font>

38:19.240 --> 38:21.398
<font color="#ffff00">Five minutes away, give or take.</font>

38:21.400 --> 38:24.158
<font color="#00ff00">Hear that? </font><font color="#00ffff">Yeah. Can you get</font>
<font color="#00ffff">there if I organise backup?</font>

38:24.160 --> 38:27.160
<font color="#00ffff">I don't want to miss him. </font><font color="#00ff00">Will do.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">No heroics.</font>

38:35.120 --> 38:36.560
<font color="#ffff00">That's his van.</font>

39:04.960 --> 39:07.880
<font color="#00ff00">Borrows his dad's tyres,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">why not his truck?</font>

39:08.880 --> 39:10.998
<font color="#ffff00">Mm-hm. </font><font color="#00ff00">I'll go find him.</font>

39:11.000 --> 39:12.920
<font color="#ffff00">I'll be the welcome party, then.</font>

39:41.960 --> 39:43.400
<font color="#00ff00">Malcolm.</font>

39:49.520 --> 39:50.680
<font color="#00ff00">Malcolm!</font>

40:01.560 --> 40:03.118
<font color="#ffff00">Ugh!</font>

40:03.120 --> 40:04.598
<font color="#00ffff">Watch out!</font>

40:04.600 --> 40:06.798
<font color="#ffffff">Hey, you, get out of there!</font>

40:06.800 --> 40:08.640
<font color="#ffffff">INDISTINCT SHOUTING</font>

40:15.240 --> 40:17.600
<font color="#ffffff">SHOUTING</font>

40:39.160 --> 40:40.320
<font color="#ffff00">Hey!</font>

40:53.120 --> 40:54.320
<font color="#ffff00">Where are you going?</font>

40:56.360 --> 40:57.520
<font color="#ffff00">Stay down.</font>

40:59.040 --> 41:00.080
<font color="#ffff00">Fresh marks.</font>

41:03.200 --> 41:07.040
<font color="#ffff00">Malcolm Wilde, I'm arresting you on</font>
<font color="#ffff00">suspicion of murder.</font>

41:48.360 --> 41:50.398
<font color="#ffff00">I'm so sorry, Pete.</font>

41:50.400 --> 41:52.398
<font color="#00ff00">I saw you at the press conference.</font>

41:52.400 --> 41:53.798
<font color="#ffff00">This is not a good idea.</font>

41:53.800 --> 41:55.160
<font color="#ffff00">You should be with Tina.</font>

42:19.040 --> 42:20.080
<font color="#ffffff">PHONE RINGS</font>

42:24.880 --> 42:26.240
<font color="#00ff00">It's Tina.</font>

42:27.240 --> 42:28.440
<font color="#ffff00">Take it.</font>

42:29.920 --> 42:31.240
<font color="#00ff00">Yeah, sweetheart?</font>

42:32.280 --> 42:33.520
<font color="#00ffff">The police have been in touch.</font>

42:34.440 --> 42:35.920
<font color="#00ffff">They've arrested Malcolm Wilde.</font>

42:44.400 --> 42:46.038
<font color="#00ffff">Jack? </font><font color="#ffff00">Yeah.</font>

42:46.040 --> 42:49.038
<font color="#00ffff">Results are back on</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Jason's histology section.</font>

42:49.040 --> 42:50.760
<font color="#00ff00">Any surprises?</font>

42:51.800 --> 42:53.998
<font color="#00ffff">On decomposition,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the body generates gases</font>

42:54.000 --> 42:56.558
<font color="#00ffff">which create bubbles in the tissue</font>
<font color="#00ffff">like so.</font>

42:56.560 --> 43:00.238
<font color="#ffff00">So far, so normal?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Yeah, and to look at</font>

43:00.240 --> 43:02.480
<font color="#00ffff">these slit-like marks are similar.</font>

43:03.560 --> 43:07.158
<font color="#00ffff">They're consistent with something</font>
<font color="#00ffff">more unusual - freezing.</font>

43:07.160 --> 43:09.040
<font color="#00ff00">Jason's body was frozen. </font><font color="#00ffff">Correct.</font>

43:10.320 --> 43:14.558
<font color="#ffff00">So the ballpark that he died four to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">six weeks ago needs to be adjusted.</font>

43:14.560 --> 43:16.398
<font color="#00ffff">Could have died months ago.</font>

43:16.400 --> 43:19.078
<font color="#00ffff">You two have just been to Wilde</font>
<font color="#00ffff">senior's residence, right?</font>

43:19.080 --> 43:21.158
<font color="#00ff00">Yeah, we've had that pleasure.</font>

43:21.160 --> 43:23.040
<font color="#00ffff">You see a freezer big enough</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to store a body?</font>

43:25.640 --> 43:27.600
<font color="#00ffff">You'd better get back out there</font>
<font color="#00ffff">then.</font>

43:31.920 --> 43:33.320
<font color="#ffffff">And your top, please.</font>

44:00.360 --> 44:01.840
<font color="#ffffff">Nasty bruises.</font>

44:22.640 --> 44:25.480
<font color="#ffff00">I was fitting an alarm box</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and I fell off my ladder.</font>

44:27.080 --> 44:28.400
<font color="#ffffff">Onto what?</font>

44:29.400 --> 44:30.520
<font color="#ffff00">Railings.</font>

44:46.680 --> 44:48.038
<font color="#ffffff">OK.</font>

44:48.040 --> 44:49.360
<font color="#ffffff">I'm done.</font>

45:46.240 --> 45:47.280
<font color="#ffff00">MacNeil!</font>

45:50.800 --> 45:51.920
<font color="#ffff00">Down here!</font>

45:53.720 --> 45:55.360
<font color="#ffff00">Downstairs.</font>

46:13.480 --> 46:16.758
<font color="#ffff00">We'll get this freighted to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the Lyell tonight.</font>

46:16.760 --> 46:21.238
<font color="#ffffff">Clothing, trace, tyre treads,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">location -</font>

46:21.240 --> 46:23.080
<font color="#ffffff">all pointing at you, Malcolm.</font>

46:24.480 --> 46:26.038
<font color="#ffff00">Someone set me up -</font>

46:26.040 --> 46:27.638
<font color="#ffff00">it's the only explanation.</font>

46:27.640 --> 46:30.358
<font color="#ffff00">Saw my name in the paper.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Your name was never in the paper -</font>

46:30.360 --> 46:32.838
<font color="#00ffff">we made sure of that.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Online then, Twitter.</font>

46:32.840 --> 46:34.678
<font color="#ffff00">You did nothing about that, did you?</font>

46:34.680 --> 46:35.998
<font color="#00ffff">Come on, Malcolm.</font>

46:36.000 --> 46:37.600
<font color="#00ffff">We both know you're guilty.</font>

46:38.880 --> 46:40.640
<font color="#00ffff">So does your dad. </font><font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

46:42.520 --> 46:44.278
<font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

46:44.280 --> 46:47.600
<font color="#ffff00">My dad believes me,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">he's the only one that does.</font>

46:50.800 --> 46:52.200
<font color="#00ffff">Let's take a break.</font>

46:59.720 --> 47:01.278
<font color="#00ffff">OK. Is that it? </font><font color="#00ff00">Yeah.</font>

47:01.280 --> 47:03.078
<font color="#00ffff">Thanks, Nikki.</font>

47:03.080 --> 47:05.758
<font color="#00ffff">I've just got a couple of questions.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">That's OK.</font>

47:05.760 --> 47:09.798
<font color="#00ffff">Can you go into a bit more detail</font>
<font color="#00ffff">about Malcolm's injuries, please?</font>

47:09.800 --> 47:11.678
<font color="#ffffff">Er, sure.</font>

47:11.680 --> 47:15.998
<font color="#ffffff">I've seen that exact bruising</font>
<font color="#ffffff">only twice before -</font>

47:16.000 --> 47:18.678
<font color="#ffffff">both times in a military context.</font>

47:18.680 --> 47:22.158
<font color="#00ffff">So, in your expert opinion,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Malcolm's lying?</font>

47:22.160 --> 47:23.838
<font color="#ffffff">About falling onto railings?</font>

47:23.840 --> 47:25.238
<font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font>

47:25.240 --> 47:28.238
<font color="#00ffff">Tell me again how you think</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the bruising was caused.</font>

47:28.240 --> 47:31.918
<font color="#ffffff">Well, I'm almost certain it's the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">result of a blanket party,</font>

47:31.920 --> 47:34.078
<font color="#ffffff">where, typically,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the victim is held down</font>

47:34.080 --> 47:36.438
<font color="#ffffff">and beaten with something like a</font>
<font color="#ffffff">sock</font>

47:36.440 --> 47:38.838
<font color="#ffffff">filled with one or more bars of</font>
<font color="#ffffff">soap.</font>

47:38.840 --> 47:41.198
<font color="#ffffff">Hurts like hell,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">but the bruising fades fast.</font>

47:41.200 --> 47:44.238
<font color="#00ffff">Yeah, still traumatic</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to be on the receiving end -</font>

47:44.240 --> 47:45.478
<font color="#00ffff">not to mention humiliating.</font>

47:45.480 --> 47:49.118
<font color="#ffffff">SLAMS TABLE</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Bullshit! Total bullshit! </font><font color="#ffff00">Hey, you!</font>

47:49.120 --> 47:50.600
<font color="#00ffff">Looks like that rang a bell.</font>

47:59.080 --> 48:00.438
<font color="#00ff00">It wasn't my dad.</font>

48:00.440 --> 48:04.160
<font color="#00ffff">What did you do to make him</font>
<font color="#00ffff">lose his temper so badly?</font>

48:10.160 --> 48:11.958
<font color="#00ff00">I told you,</font>

48:11.960 --> 48:13.638
<font color="#00ff00">I fell on a railing.</font>

48:13.640 --> 48:14.840
<font color="#ffffff">KNOCK AT DOOR</font>

48:17.000 --> 48:18.520
<font color="#ffffff">Can I speak to you?</font>

48:21.440 --> 48:23.998
<font color="#00ffff">I think his dad beat the truth</font>
<font color="#00ffff">out of him.</font>

48:24.000 --> 48:25.638
<font color="#ffffff">What the hell was that? </font><font color="#00ffff">What?</font>

48:25.640 --> 48:28.318
<font color="#ffffff">Why didn't you just ask me</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to say that to his face?</font>

48:28.320 --> 48:32.318
<font color="#00ffff">Because I knew you'd say no.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I'm not your puppet!</font>

48:32.320 --> 48:34.958
<font color="#ffffff">It's not my fault you're desperate</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and he's not cracking.</font>

48:34.960 --> 48:37.398
<font color="#00ffff">Look at the forensics.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Asking me to Jason's parents'</font>

48:37.400 --> 48:39.758
<font color="#ffffff">I thought was unorthodox,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">but well-meant.</font>

48:39.760 --> 48:41.558
<font color="#ffffff">Tricking me into menacing a suspect,</font>

48:41.560 --> 48:43.998
<font color="#ffffff">that is something else entirely!</font>
<font color="#00ffff">He did it, Nikki,</font>

48:44.000 --> 48:47.038
<font color="#00ffff">and I will do whatever it takes to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">get it over the line with the CPS.</font>

48:47.040 --> 48:50.558
<font color="#ffffff">"Whatever it takes"? </font><font color="#00ffff">It's either</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that or he walks free again.</font>

48:50.560 --> 48:52.278
<font color="#ffffff">If I get adversarial,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I'm compromised.</font>

48:52.280 --> 48:54.398
<font color="#ffffff">Perspective and integrity</font>
<font color="#ffffff">go out of the window</font>

48:54.400 --> 48:55.840
<font color="#ffffff">and then I'm no good to anyone.</font>

48:57.600 --> 48:59.318
